snippet.title: 'Vessel' Invention Report 2 - Seeds
snippet.description:
'Vessel' launches March 1st on PC, available on Steam and http://www.StrangeLoopGames.com

Coming soon on console.

Invention report #1, Fluros: www.youtube.com/watch?v=gbPEE0tht-Q
Invention reports #3 The Accelerator: coming soon.

Homepage: http://www.StrangeLoopGames.com/
Follow us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/VesselGame
Twitter: http://twitter.com/StrangeLoopGame

'First look' developer walkthrough here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=24Yubu615mE

Official trailer here:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kmwidqe1T4A

Music is from the Vessel soundtrack.  Jon Hopkins - Vessel
